raw: I-70 E Shut Down, One Critically Injured in Fiery Multi-Car Crash, Grass Fire at I-70 E & I-635 N, Kansas City, Kansas, 66102

-NNBnqZdR7dw0DHfUCht.text: According to reports from KMBC, a fiery multi-vehicle collision on I-70 E near I-635 has resulted in at least one person with life-threatening injuries and the highway being shut down.

-NNBnqa7ZNBmXLjZ3JA0.text: Incident reported at I-70 E & I-635 N.

-NNBoH2gYbYESVp7xUOu.text: A grass fire has also been ignited by the crash. Traffic is being redirected off of I-70 E to N 57th St.
